		<h3>Pathway to Industry Symposium</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>Date: Saturday, February 25, 2017</li>
			<li>Time: 8:30 AM</li>
			<li>Location: The University Club, <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/SjWU1jJk8ju"> 123 University Pl, Pittsburgh, PA 15260</a> </li>
		</ul>
		<p> Please join the Student Industry Organization for a Pharmaceutical Industry Symposium on Saturday, February 25th, 2017 at the University Club starting at 8:30 AM. This event will feature guest speakers, a keynote speakers, and various interactive activities. The symposium is open to students from all classes in the School of Pharmacy as well as PhD program students! Please join us for a great day of pharmaceutical industry networking. Dress is business casual (no leggings, no white coats) and please bring your nametag from P1 year if you still have it.  Breakfast and lunch will be provided! </p>

		<p>This half-day symposium will feature:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Breakfast</li>
			<li>Speaker Introductions</li>
			<li>Keynote Speaker</li>
			<li>Lunch (hot buffet)</li>
			<li>Applying for Fellowships</li>
			<li>Round Tables</li>
		</ul>

